IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. GOTO-COMPUTABLE-EXITS-LOOP.

DATA DIVISION.
01 TARGET-FIELD PICTURE IS X(20).

PROCEDURE DIVISION.
MOVE "DONE" TO TARGET-FIELD
LOOP
    DISPLAY "LOOP BEFORE COMPUTED GOTO"
    GO TO TARGET-FIELD
    DISPLAY "LOOP AFTER COMPUTED GOTO"
END.

DONE.
DISPLAY "DONE AFTER COMPUTED LOOP"
STOP.
